data.description:
Charming 2 bedroom / 2 bath / 2 car garage house nestled in a desirable 24-hour guarded gated community now available to you!!!!

This property offers an amazing opportunity for adult country club living in a vibrant 55+ community.

As you enter the home, you'll be captivated by the stunning golf course view that stretches beyond the backyard. Imagine sipping your morning coffee on the enclosed lanai while enjoying the picturesque scenery.

The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the living spaces, making it great for entertaining friends and family. The eat-in kitchen offers ample counter space and white appliances.

Vaulted ceilings add an airy and spacious feel to the home, enhancing its overall appeal. The large master suite is a peaceful retreat, offering privacy, tranquility and leads out to your covered lanai overlooking the golf course.

Living in this community means resort-style living at its finest. The clubhouse provides endless opportunities for socializing, with a restaurant and bar where you can gather with neighbors and friends. Access to tennis courts, an 18-hole championship golf course and more! If dancing is your passion, there are regular dance events to enjoy. And don't forget about the pro golf shop for all your golfing needs.

Located in a prime location, this property offers convenient access to nearby amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, and recreational facilities.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in a welcoming community that offers an abundance of amenities and activities. Schedule your showing today and embrace the joys of adult country club living!!!!
